snippet.title: Footage of canceled Xbox game Archipelago (AKA Knights of Decayden)
snippet.description:
This clip was shared with us by Totally Games founder Larry Holland. The game was meant to be a Microsoft-published Xbox exclusive released within a year of the original console's 2001 launch. But it was cancelled in early 2002. 

Totally Games built on their experience making acclaimed Star Wars flight combat games. Read more about it on Axios.com
